::: {#4b7ddeea .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

# plotting the line chart
sns.lineplot(df, y="sepal_width", x=df.index)

# showing the plot
plt.show()
```

