# Adding interaction

Untuk memunculkan tombol-tombol interaktif pada plot, kita menggunakan submodule dari library plotly yaitu `plotly.graph_objects`

## Dropdown Menu

::: {#cd0d0cf7 .cell execution_count=20}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import plotly.graph_objects as go

plot = go.Figure(data=[go.Scatter(
    x=df['day'],
    y=df['tip'],
    mode='markers',)
])

# Add dropdown
plot.update_layout(
    updatemenus=[
        dict(buttons=list([
            dict(
                args=["type", "scatter"],
                label="Scatter Plot",
                method="restyle"
            ),
            dict(
                args=["type", "bar"],
                label="Bar Chart",
                method="restyle"
            )
        ]),
            direction="down",
        ),
    ]
)

plot.show()
```

